The Purposes of processing

Legal Ground of the processing

A) To provide you with all the functionality of our Application.

B) To provide you with Application, adapted for your device, display and firmware.

 

A) Your Consent.

B) The processing is necessary for the purposes of the legitimate interests pursued by Us.

